value: Breeds ne China and Japan; winters to India and SE Asia
Breeds in Mongoha, China south to the Yangtse Valley, Manchuria, Korea and Japan. Winters in southern China, eastern India, Burma, Malay States and Indo-Chinese countries.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: breeds in undisturbed areas of swamps, near rivers and rice fields;in winter also in wet habitats, e.g.marshes, riverbanks, wet grasslands, rice stubble, jheels, ploughed fields
